            "   • Quick access to common operations\n\n" +
            
            "🏠 ROOM MANAGEMENT\n" +
            "   • Add, edit, or delete room information\n" +
            "   • Update room status (Available/Occupied/Maintenance/Reserved/Cleaning)\n" +
            "   • Set room pricing and amenities\n" +
            "   • View room availability in real-time\n\n" +
            
            "👥 GUEST MANAGEMENT\n" +
            "   • Register new guests with complete details\n" +
            "   • Update guest information and preferences\n" +
